<activity xml:id="act-fraccionesQueTienenElMismoNumerador" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li><ol>
<li>
<m>\frac{1}{3}</m>. Sample response:
<p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p>
<img alt="Diagram." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158751.svg"/>
<p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p>
<img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/>
<p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p>
<img alt="Diagram." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158751.svg" width="80%"/>
</li>
<li>
<m>\frac{3}{4}</m>. Sample response: One fourth is twice the size of 1 eighth, so 3 fourths must be twice the size of 3 eighths.</li>
<li>
<m>\frac{5}{3}</m>. Sample response:
<p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p>
<img alt="Number lines." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158752.svg"/>
<p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p>
<img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/>
<p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p>
<img alt="Number lines." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158752.svg" width="80%"/>
</li>
<li>
<m>\frac{9}{6}</m>. Sample response: One sixth is larger than 1 eighth, so 9 sixths is greater than 9 eighths.</li>
</ol>
      </li>
      <li><ol>
<li>&gt;</li>
<li>&gt;</li>
<li>&lt;</li>
<li>&lt;</li>
</ol>
      </li>
      <li><ol>
<li>Any denominator less than 3.</li>
<li>Any denominator greater than 4.</li>
<li>Any denominator less than 4.</li>
<li>Any denominator less than 6.</li>
</ol>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


